<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Operational modules</p>
      <h1>Module Mode</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Module Mode shows how the operational systems demo can grow beyond booking intake
        into records, invoice workflows and admin-facing infrastructure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <article class="stat">
        <strong><%= stats.recordsTotal %></strong>
        <span>Demo records</span>
      </article>
      <article class="stat">
        <strong><%= stats.recordsActive %></strong>
        <span>Active records</span>
      </article>
      <article class="stat">
        <strong><%= stats.invoicesTotal %></strong>
        <span>Demo invoices</span>
      </article>
      <article class="stat">
        <strong><%= stats.invoicesOpen %></strong>
        <span>Open invoices</span>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid module-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Skeleton module</p>
        <h3>Records Module</h3>
        <p>
          Public-safe record list and detail views showing how client/project records
          could be organised inside an operational system.
        </p>
        <a class="btn" href="/modules/records">Open records module</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Skeleton module</p>
        <h3>Invoice Workflow</h3>
        <p>
          Demo invoice list, status states, detail view and export route prepared
          as a foundation for future operational workflow expansion.
        </p>
        <a class="btn" href="/modules/invoices">Open invoice workflow</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Current complete module</p>
        <h3>Booking Workflow</h3>
        <p>
          The current working module includes public intake, confirmation,
          admin review, status handling and CSV export.
        </p>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/admin">Open booking admin</a>
        <a class="text-link" href="/modules/workflow">View workflow overview</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Reporting layer</p>
        <h3>Reports & Export Capability</h3>
        <p>
          Summary metrics and export routes show how operational data can support finance,
          admin review and decision-making.
        </p>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/modules/reports">Open reports view</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
